# RBO Trade Intelligence v2.0
### Rice Bran Crude Oil — Complete Trading Platform PWA

> **Live URL**: https://rishabh27-blip.github.io/trade-engine/

---

## 🧠 What This Is

A **Progressive Web App** (installable on phone/desktop) that gives rice bran crude oil traders a complete intelligence system:

| Module | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| 📊 Price Range Estimator | Lead-lag model: FCPO + CBOT ZL → RBO containment zone |
| 🎯 Trade Engine | 100-pt risk scoring + position sizing + trade logging |
| 📈 Dashboard | Equity curve, win rate, profit factor, Sharpe ratio |
| 🛡 Risk Manager | Kelly criterion, position sizing, drawdown control |
| 💼 Financials | P&L ledger, cost structure, margin tracking |
| 🔮 Scenarios | Bear/Base/Bull case + break-even + sensitivity |
| 🚛 Operations | Physical lot tracking, storage aging, dispatch log |
| 📄 Reports | Executive summary + CSV export + print-ready |

---

## ⚡ Deploy in 5 Minutes

### Step 1 — Upload to GitHub

1. Go to your existing repo: `https://github.com/rishabh27-blip/trade-engine`
2. **Delete all existing files** (or upload to a fresh repo)
3. Upload **all files** from this folder (maintain folder structure exactly)
4. Commit to `main` branch

### Step 2 — Enable GitHub Actions + Pages

1. In your repo → **Settings** → **Actions** → **General**
2. Set "Workflow permissions" to **Read and write permissions**
3. Click Save

4. In your repo → **Settings** → **Pages**
5. Under "Build and deployment" → Source: **Deploy from a branch**
6. Branch: **`gh-pages`** → folder: **`/ (root)`**
7. Click Save

### Step 3 — Trigger Deploy

```bash
# Option A: Push any change to main
git push origin main

# Option B: Manual trigger
# GitHub repo → Actions → Deploy to GitHub Pages → Run workflow
```

### Step 4 — Install on Phone

**Android (Chrome):**
1. Open `https://rishabh27-blip.github.io/trade-engine/`
2. Chrome menu (⋮) → "Add to Home Screen" or "Install App"
3. Tap Install ✅

**iPhone (Safari):**
1. Open URL in **Safari** (not Chrome)
2. Share button (⬆️) → "Add to Home Screen"
3. Tap Add ✅

