## 📊 The Price Range Model

### Lead-Lag Pipeline

```
FCPO (MYR/ton) ──┐
                  ├─→ Combined Signal ──→ Expected Move ──→ [Lower, Mid, Upper]
CBOT ZL (¢/lb) ──┘
```

### Formulas

```
FCPO%          = (Close - Prev Close) / Prev Close × 100
ZL%            = (Close - Prev Close) / Prev Close × 100
CombinedSignal = (0.6 × FCPO%) + (0.4 × ZL%)

Volatility Multiplier:
  |Signal| > 1.0%  →  1.5×   (HIGH vol)
  |Signal| > 0.5%  →  1.2×   (MEDIUM vol)
  else             →  0.8×   (LOW/compressed)

5D Avg Range   = (5D High - 5D Low) / 2
ExpectedMove   = (Signal / 100) × YestPrice × 0.5 [lag dampener]
MidPrice       = YestPrice + ExpectedMove
Upper          = Mid + (AvgRange × Multiplier)
Lower          = Mid − (AvgRange × Multiplier)
```

### Trade Signals

| Condition | Signal |
|-----------|--------|
| Range < ₹1/kg | ❌ NO TRADE |
| \|Signal\| > 0.8% | 📈 BREAKOUT BIAS |
| \|Signal\| ≤ 0.8% | 🔄 MEAN REVERSION BIAS |

---

## 🎯 Trade Scoring System (100 pts)

| Factor | Max | Criteria |
|--------|-----|---------|
| Margin/kg | 30 | >₹3=30, >₹2=25, >₹1=18, >0=8 |
| Risk vs Margin | 30 | <30% margin=30, <50%=24, <100%=16 |
| Holding Days | 20 | ≤1 day=20, ≤2=18, ≤4=12 |
| Reliability | 20 | 4 pts/star (max 5 stars) |

**Thresholds:**
- 72+ → ✅ STRONG TRADE (100% size)
- 60–71 → ✅ TRADE (75% size)
- 50–59 → ⚠️ CONSIDER (50% size)
- <50 → ❌ NO TRADE

---

## 🛡 Risk Management Rules

- **Max risk per trade**: Default 1.5% of capital (configurable)
- **Kelly Criterion**: Live calculation from your trade history
- **Stop trading if**: Drawdown > 15%
- **Never**: Average a losing position
- **Minimum**: Win rate ≥ 45%, Profit Factor ≥ 1.0

---

## 💾 Data & Privacy

- **100% local** — all data in browser localStorage
- **No server** — nothing transmitted anywhere
- **No accounts** — use immediately
- **Backup**: Use the Export CSV button regularly

