## 🔧 Local Development

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start dev server
npm run dev

# Build for production
npm run build

# Preview production build
npm run preview
```

---

## 🖼 Icons (Important!)

Place your 192×192 and 512×512 PNG icons in `public/icons/`:
- `public/icons/icon-192.png`
- `public/icons/icon-512.png`

If missing, the app still works but won't have a custom icon on mobile.

**Quick fix**: Use the icons from your previous PWA build.

